extendedInfo.description: Are you a Kanye West fan?  Listen to your favorite Kanye West songs, some in collaboration with Jay-Z.  Songs & Lyrics including:- All Falls Down- All Of The Lights- Amazing- Blame Game- Can't Tell Me Nothing- Coldest Winter- Dark Fantasy- Diamonds From Sierra Leone- Flashing Lights- Gold Digger- Good Life- Good Morning- H*A*M- Heard 'Em Say- Heartless- Homecoming- Jesus Walks- Lost In The World- Love Lockdown- Mercy- Ni**as In Paris- No Church In The Wild- Otis- Paranoid- POWER- Runaway- Stronger- The New Workout Plan- Touch The Sky- Two Words- Welcome To HeartbreakTo keep this app free, the song videos are from Youtube.  Internet connection is needed to play the videos.  Due to the nature of some Youtube videos, you may be required to login in your Youtube application in order to view some of the videos.This app is supported via search. Please note that the following will be added to your device once you download the app â Search icon, bookmark link and browser homepage. You can delete/replace these search points easily.
